18.	Match strings that contain no spaces.
Example: "NoSpaceHere" âœ… "has space" âŒ

19.	Match strings that do not start with a digit (using lookahead or negation).
Example: "abc1" âœ… "1abc" âŒ
20.	Match a password: at least 8 chars, one uppercase, one lowercase, one digit, one special symbol.
21.	Match words that have double vowels (like â€œcoolâ€, â€œbeetâ€).
22.	Match all email addresses in a paragraph (global match).
23.	Match all HTML tags in a string (e.g. <div>, <p>).
24.	Match duplicate consecutive words (e.g. â€œis isâ€, â€œthe theâ€).
