o	At least 8 characters
o	One lowercase
o	One uppercase
o	One digit
o	One special character
(use multiple lookaheads)
14.	Find all numbers that are not preceded by $ (negative lookbehind).
15.	Match an email only if itâ€™s inside angle brackets â€” e.g., <abc@xyz.com>.
16.	Match words not followed by punctuation (negative lookahead).
